Reuter shares registered with U . S . SEC . Reuters Holdings Plc filed a shelf registration statement with U . S . regulators for up to 7 , 589 , 557 ordinary shares in connection with a Daily Mail & General Trust Plc exchangeable bond offering . The filing relates to Daily Mail ' s issuance of bonds that are exchangeable into Reuter shares at any time between Aug 11 and September 21 , 2004 . The 2 . 5 percent exchangeable bonds due 2004 were offered for sale on June 5 . Reuters will not receive any proceeds from the exchange . 
